'''Monkey-lizards''' were an ape-like [[Reptile/Legends|reptile]] species that was native to the jungles found on [[Tenupe]]. These monkey-lizards were distinctly different from the [[Kowakian monkey-lizard/Legends|Kowakian monkey-lizard]] species.

